original_title: Greg Proops: Live at Musso & Frank
overview: Greg Proops takes you to a time when people drank gin for lunch and Robert Mitchum's house was the medical marijuana dispensary. Live at Musso and Frank is the first ever comedy special recorded at Hollywood's most historic and legendary bar and grill.
tagline: Comedy recorded in the place where organized crime used to have its prom.
title: Greg Proops: Live at Musso & Frank
